## Curriculum source-of-truth rule

All curriculum/business data must be updated from the shared source of truth.

Do not fix curriculum only in Flutter.
Do not fix curriculum only in Web.

If changing:
- learning language catalog
- native language behavior
- lesson/unit/module/niche tree
- exercise types
- lesson content
- Plus gating
- AI Q&A rules
- translations
- validator rules

then update shared source-of-truth first, then regenerate/sync outputs for both Web and Flutter.

Do not manually patch generated JSON only. Fix the source/generator/schema first, then regenerate.

Current curriculum model:

NovaLang Curriculum
├── Core Foundation
├── 15 Main Niches
└── Exam Preparation, future branch only

Current build scope:
- Keep 20 learning languages in catalog.
- Only English and Japanese are playable for now.
- The other 18 languages must be preview / comingSoon.
- Build only Daily Life → Greetings → Unit 1 for English and Japanese first.
- Do not expand beyond that until the user reviews.

Lesson structure:
Each lesson must have exactly 10 exercises.

Exercise 1–7:
- Free
- fixed/non-AI exercises

Exercise 8:
- Plus only
- Listening Gap-fill
- uses device TTS / speechText
- no AI API

Exercise 9:
- Plus only
- Controlled AI Q&A for the 390 yen/month Plus plan
- not open-ended chat
- 1 set = AI asks 1 short lesson-based question → user answers → AI gives short correction/comment → set ends
- keep output short and cost-controlled
- do not save long chat history

Exercise 10:
- Plus only
- AI Feedback / Review
- should reuse Exercise 9 feedback
- must not trigger an extra AI call by default

Native language rule:
Native language controls meanings, explanations, hints, and answer options.
Supported native languages:
vi, en, ja, ko, zh

Example:
nativeLanguage = ja, learningLanguage = en
chooseMeaning options must be Japanese.

Example:
nativeLanguage = vi, learningLanguage = ja
chooseMeaning options must be Vietnamese.

Validator must fail if:
- lesson does not have exactly 10 exercises
- Exercise 8–10 are not Plus gated
- Exercise 9 is open-ended chat
- translations vi/en/ja/ko/zh are missing
- Japanese reading/romanization/speechText is missing
- chooseMeaning options are in the wrong native language
- duplicate options exist
- unsupported exercise types are used

Required checks:
npm run generate:curriculum
npm run validate:curriculum
npm run sync:flutter-assets
npm run build

Then:
cd mobile/novalang_flutter
flutter analyze
flutter build apk --debug

Reporting rule:
After each task, report briefly in Vietnamese.
Max 8 bullet lines total.
Do not paste full code unless asked.
Stop and ask for review before expanding.